      "widgets_values": [
        "Create a realistic full-body photo.\n\nUse the identity reference through PuLID only for the person's face identity and facial structure.\n\nUse the outfit/pose reference for clothing design, colors, fabric texture, accessories, body pose, body framing, and background.\n\nThe final image must show the same person identity from the identity reference wearing the outfit from the outfit/pose reference and adopting the pose from the outfit/pose reference.\n\nDo not copy clothing from the identity reference. Do not copy the face, hair, or identity from the outfit/pose reference. Preserve the outfit colors, patterns, collar, sleeves, hem, shoes, and accessories. Natural lighting, coherent anatomy, realistic hands."
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
